    {
      "id": 28651,
      "category": "researcher",
      "content": "During my research on the TikTok Ads portal I found a RCE thought the video creation process resulting to a root access on the system mainly due to a misconfugration ffmpeg. A simple id and ls commands results were reported and the TikTok team fixed the weakness quickly.",
